insert into casemap_documents (id, kind, label, document_text, metadata) values ('case:hksar_v_harman_preet', 'case', 'HKSAR v Harman Preet', 'HKSAR v Harman Preet [5-21] In HKSAR v Harman Preet ,28 the defendant was convicted of murder. At the time of the killing, the defendant was 2 weeks short of his 18th birthday. The trial judge 29 sentenced him to life imprisonment with the minimum term to be served stipulated at 25 years. In allowing the appeal against the sentence and reducing the minimum term to be served to 24 Contrary to section 47C of OAPO. See also section 47B of OAPO which creates an offence of ‘chil...', '{"type": "case", "label": "HKSAR v Harman Preet", "keywords": ["hksar", "harman", "preet", "was", "see", "defendant"]}'::jsonb) on conflict (id) do update set kind = excluded.kind, label = excluded.label, document_text = excluded.document_text, metadata = excluded.metadata;
